@startuml
actor "门店人员" as StoreStaff
participant "钉钉门店宝" as DingTalkStore
participant "报货中心" as OrderCenter

StoreStaff -> DingTalkStore: 申报货物
DingTalkStore -> OrderCenter: 下发申报货物单据
activate OrderCenter
OrderCenter -> OrderCenter: 单据数据校验
OrderCenter -> OrderCenter: 单据储存
deactivate OrderCenter
OrderCenter --> DingTalkStore
DingTalkStore --> StoreStaff
@enduml